-the-war-in-gaza-has-to-end/0000018d-f621-d72b-a18d-f7f12cd10000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 146 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-146/0000018d-f60b-dd0a-afcf-ffdfcfdf0000</link><description>哈马斯和以色列国防军对加沙中部 110 多名等待粮食援助的巴勒斯坦人死亡的说法相互矛盾 ■ 拜登：周一不太可能达成协议 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：自战争开始以来，已有 30,000 多名加沙人丧生，70,000 多人受伤 ■ 联合国人权高专办酋长：各方都犯下了战争罪行 ■ 战争开始146天后，你需要知道这些</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 18:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-146/0000018d-f60b-dd0a-afcf-ffdfcfdf0000</guid></item><item><title>无法超越“罗”！袋鼠性格诠释赢得“舞蹈你的博士”竞赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-29/ty-article/cant-outdo-the-roo-interpretation-of-kangaroo-personalities-wins-dance-your-phd-contest/0000018d-f4ec-d401-a3dd-fdfe6cba0000</link><description>“未经编排的混搭”诠释舞蹈呈现了灰袋鼠独特性格的博士学位，跨越了社会科学和物理学，因为袋鼠</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 17:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-29/ty-article/cant-outdo-the-roo-interpretation-of-kangaroo-personalities-wins-dance-your-phd-contest/0000018d-f4ec-d401-a3dd-fdfe6cba0000</guid></item><item><title>人身安全和制度种族主义：阿拉伯裔以色列市长面临的挑战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/personal-safety-institutional-racism-the-challenges-facing-arab-israeli-mayors/0000018d-f51f-da4e-adbf-f7bff1b20000</link><description>新当选的市政领导人必须与以色列历史上最极端的政府抗衡。当他们当选所要服务的公众向他们寻求答案时，许多挑战等待着他们</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 15:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/personal-safety-institutional-racism-the-challenges-facing-arab-israeli-mayors/0000018d-f51f-da4e-adbf-f7bff1b20000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列的未来有一个愿景。内塔尼亚胡不</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.