怀疑论者回应，年代测定完全错误，宝石可能已被交易</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 12:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-29/ty-article/rare-phoenician-pendant-found-in-jerusalem-but-is-it-linked-to-king-solomon/0000018d-f47e-d401-a3dd-fd7ef50c0000</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，美国年轻人现在比长辈更有可能相信对犹太人的负面刻板印象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-more-likely-than-their-elders-to-believe-negative-stereotypes-about-jews/0000018d-f419-dd0a-afcf-ffdf8a5a0000</link><description>ADL 的一项新调查询问受访者是否认为犹太人对以色列比对美国更忠诚，他们是否认为犹太人比其他人更愿意利用不正当手段来获得他们想要的东西，以及他们是否认为犹太人对华尔街有太多控制权</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-more-likely-than-their-elders-to-believe-negative-stereotypes-about-jews/0000018d-f419-dd0a-afcf-ffdf8a5a0000</guid></item><item><title>CNN：拜登政府担心，如果外交失败，以色列可能在春末入侵黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/report-u-s-concerned-israel-may-invade-lebanon-in-late-spring-if-diplomacy-fails/0000018d-f3f7-d7f4-a3dd-f7ff42ce0000</link><description>拜登政府一名高级官员表示，“我们的行动假设以色列将在未来几个月内采取军事行动”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/report-u-s-concerned-israel-may-invade-lebanon-in-late-spring-if-diplomacy-fails/0000018d-f3f7-d7f4-a3dd-f7ff42ce0000</guid></item><item><title>当局称，30,000 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙被杀，其中包括 12,500 名儿童和青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/30-000-palestinians-killed-in-gaza-hamas-says-as-hunger-and-despair-spread/0000018d-ef7f-d1e0-a1dd-ffff13100000</link><description>然而，这些数字并未代表死亡总数，因为据信整个加沙地带约有 8,000 名失踪者被埋在废墟下。无国界医生组织表示，“心理伤害导致五岁的孩子告诉我们他们宁愿死”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/3